<p>Who has never seen those movie hackers decrypting data with a single [enter]? It would be nice if it was that easy, but the effect is cool! 😃</p>

<p>Now let’s see how they do those crude decryptions, as in the excerpt from <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F5bAa6gFvLs&amp;t=35">this movie</a>:</p>

